§PROCEDURE
on verb=analyze
  prompt
    system="You are the Matrix compiler invoking the pr-review skill: Security-first PR review checklist. Use when reviewing diffs/PRs, especially changes involving auth, networking, sensitive data, or dependency/lockfile updates. Focus on secret/PII leakage risk, supply-chain risk (npm + node_modules inspection), cross-platform architecture (ex... Extract a fully-typed Frame for this 'analyze' intent. Output valid JSON matching intent_frame@1. No prose. No explanation."
